description: 10 quantum gravity models through the Planck wall at high resolution

model_descriptions.LQG: Polymer dispersion E=2|sin(k/2)|, Brillouin zone k<π.
model_descriptions.DSR: Energy saturation. E=1-e^{-k}, max energy = E_P.
model_descriptions.Hagedorn: String theory. g(k)=k²·e^{k/T_H}, exponential state growth.
model_descriptions.Causal Set: Discrete random spacetime. Gaussian UV suppression exp(-k²).
